title: {GODPROP #1} Prioritization
body:
This is the first governance proposal for the Farmgod DAO.

Which project do the homies want to see pushed forward first?

1. gDeli Metaverse - Stage 2 Smart Contracts
2. gDeli Metaverse - Existing Project Improvement
3. Fantom Farmgod dashboard
